                <input type="radio" name="options" id="option1" autocomplete="off" checked> RB
            </label>
            <label class="btn btn-primary">
                <input type="radio" name="options" id="option2" autocomplete="off"> RB
            </label>
            <label class="btn btn-primary">
                <input type="radio" name="options" id="option2" autocomplete="off"> JJ
            </label>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="patternDescription">
            <br />
            <p><b>Example</b>: Golf is <i><b>not</b></i> <i><b>so</b></i> <i><b>easy</b></i> as one may think.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<br />
